00:20:44,390 --> 00:20:49,592
1668. The church kidnapped
four Illuminati scientists

250
00:20:49,807 --> 00:20:52,690
and branded each one of them on the
chest with the symbol of the cross.

251
00:20:53,035 --> 00:20:55,588
To 'purge' them of their
sins and they executed them,

252
00:20:56,260 --> 00:20:57,970
threw their bodies out in the street

253
00:20:58,151 --> 00:20:59,708
as a warning to others
to stop questioning

254
00:20:59,908 --> 00:21:02,115
church rulings on scientific
matters. They radicalized them.

255
00:21:02,296 --> 00:21:06,247
The Purga created a darker,
more violent Illuminati.

256
00:21:06,427 --> 00:21:08,826
One bent on... on retribution.

257
00:21:09,492 --> 00:21:12,417
And look how they intend to
finally get it. Using anti-matter.

258
00:21:12,685 --> 00:21:16,682
Technology to destroy the church.
Science obliterates religion.

259
00:21:18,325 --> 00:21:19,411
Is there any more?

260
00:21:21,429 --> 00:21:24,054
...and sacrifice them
on the altars of science.

261
00:21:24,304 --> 00:21:26,934
Then bring your church down upon you.

262
00:21:27,168 --> 00:21:30,488
Vatican City will be consumed by light.

263
00:21:31,037 --> 00:21:35,173
A shining star at the end
of the Path of Illumination.

264
00:21:35,373 --> 00:21:36,724
Path of Illumination?

265
00:21:40,549 --> 00:21:42,349
I need access to the Vatican archives.

266
00:21:44,657 --> 00:21:46,526
Professor, I don't think this
is the appropriate moment--

267
00:21:46,708 --> 00:21:48,931
Your petition has been
denied seven times.

268
00:21:49,124 --> 00:21:51,011
No, no. This has-
This has nothing to do with my work.

269
00:21:51,012 --> 00:21:53,697
The Path of Illumination
is a hidden trail through Rome itself

270
00:21:53,698 --> 00:21:55,529
that leads to the
Church of the Illumination.

271
00:21:55,714 --> 00:21:58,055
The place where the Illuminati
would meet in secret.

272
00:21:58,303 --> 00:22:03,528
If I can find the "Segno", the sign,
that marks the beginning of that path,

273
00:22:04,419 --> 00:22:05,672
the four churches along it.

274
00:22:05,673 --> 00:22:08,039
It may be where he intends
to murder your Cardinals.

275
00:22:08,374 --> 00:22:13,709
One every hour. At 8, 9, 10 and 11.
Then the device explodes at midnight.

276
00:22:14,327 --> 00:22:17,624
If we could figure out the first
church and get there before he does,

277
00:22:17,813 --> 00:22:19,034
maybe we could stop it.

278
00:22:19,212 --> 00:22:22,280
But I can't find the start of the
path until I get into the archives.

279
00:22:23,818 --> 00:22:25,392
Even if I wanted to help you,

280
00:22:25,551 --> 00:22:27,474
access to the archives
is only by written decree

281
00:22:27,661 --> 00:22:30,177
by the curator on the
Board of Vatican Librarians.

282
00:22:30,734 --> 00:22:32,590
Or by papal mandate.

283
00:22:32,763 --> 00:22:35,672
Yes, but, as you no doubt have
heard, the Holy Father is dead.

284
00:22:36,925 --> 00:22:38,507
What about il Camerlengo?

285
00:22:38,661 --> 00:22:41,483
The Camerlengo is just a priest
here. The former pope's chamberlain.

286
00:22:41,656 --> 00:22:45,112
Doesn't the power of the Holy See rest
in him during "Tempo Sede Vacante"?

287
00:22:53,122 --> 00:22:55,393
Fellas, you called me.

288
00:22:57,499 --> 00:22:58,862
His Holiness once told me

289
00:22:59,035 --> 00:23:02,151
the Pope is a man torn between
the real world and the divine.

290
00:23:02,834 --> 00:23:05,093
It seems the real world
is upon us tonight.

291
00:23:06,764 --> 00:23:09,936
I'm familiar with Illuminati lore
and the legend of the brandings.

292
00:23:10,570 --> 00:23:13,002
The Purga is a dark stain
on this church's history.

293
00:23:13,856 --> 00:23:16,160
I'm not surprised this ghost
has returned to haunt us.

294
00:23:18,985 --> 00:23:22,365
Commandante, have you begun a
search for this explosive device?

295
00:23:22,582 --> 00:23:24,135
Of course, but it could be anywhere.

296
00:23:24,293 --> 00:23:26,684
My primary concern at the moment
is the safety of the cardinals.

297
00:23:26,875 --> 00:23:28,561
The Sistine Chapel is a fortress.

298
00:23:29,007 --> 00:23:30,871
As long as the cardinals
are in conclave,

299
00:23:30,872 --> 00:23:32,601
your security concerns
are at a minimum.

300
00:23:33,598 --> 00:23:34,910
Devote as many of your people--

301
00:23:35,130 --> 00:23:37,198
Signore, if you are about to suggest
a naked eye search

302
00:23:37,199 --> 00:23:38,896
of the entire Vatican City,
I will tell you...

303
00:23:38,897 --> 00:23:40,114
- Commander.
- ... I do not have the people.

304
00:23:40,299 --> 00:23:42,379
Although I am not His Holiness,

305
00:23:42,562 --> 00:23:44,934
when you are addressing me,
you are addressing this office.

306
00:23:44,935 --> 00:23:45,866
Do you understand?

307
00:23:47,713 --> 00:23:50,253
- Yes, Father.
- Good.

308
00:23:51,806 --> 00:23:54,953
Now, you said the image on the screen
was illuminated by artificial light.

309
00:23:56,023 --> 00:23:59,709
Might I suggest methodically cutting
power to various sections of the city?

310
00:24:00,323 --> 00:24:01,895
When the image on the
screen goes dark,

311
00:24:01,896 --> 00:24:04,097
you'll have a more specific
idea of the camera's location.

312
00:24:08,384 --> 00:24:11,575
Dr. Vetra, beside yourself
and your research partner,

313
00:24:11,809 --> 00:24:14,060
who else knew about
this antimatter project?

314
00:24:15,121 --> 00:24:16,666
No one but the research team.

315
00:24:17,606 --> 00:24:19,405
This project was strictly confidential.

316
00:24:19,780 --> 00:24:21,641
But Silvano kept detailed journals.

317
00:24:21,642 --> 00:24:24,604
If he told anyone else
about what we were doing,

318
00:24:24,605 --> 00:24:25,938
he would have made a note of it.

319
00:24:26,272 --> 00:24:27,661
And do you have these journals?

320
00:24:27,847 --> 00:24:29,793
I can have them flown here
from Geneva in an hour.

321
00:24:30,227 --> 00:24:31,130
Please.

322
00:24:33,173 --> 00:24:34,124
Professor Langdon.

323
00:24:45,490 --> 00:24:47,315
Mr. Langdon.

324
00:24:47,590 --> 00:24:50,285
You are correct that I may
grant you access to the archives.

325
00:24:52,662 --> 00:24:54,010
Thank you, Padre.

326
00:24:54,225 --> 00:24:57,687
I said that you are correct that I may,
not- not that I will.

327
00:24:59,886 --> 00:25:02,840
Christianity's most sacred
codes are in that archive.

328
00:25:04,206 --> 00:25:07,220
Given your recent
entanglement with the church,

329
00:25:07,426 --> 00:25:11,281
there is a question I'd like to ask you
first, here, in the office of His Holiness.

330
00:25:18,635 --> 00:25:19,877
Do you believe in God, Sir?

331
00:25:23,724 --> 00:25:27,643
Father, I simply
believe that religion...

332
00:25:27,859 --> 00:25:30,355
I did not ask you if you
believe what man says about God.

333
00:25:31,236 --> 00:25:32,673
I asked if you believe in God.

334
00:25:35,957 --> 00:25:37,353
I'm an academic.

335
00:25:38,665 --> 00:25:42,977
My mind tells me I will
never understand God.

336
00:25:44,166 --> 00:25:45,405
And your heart?

337
00:25:48,317 --> 00:25:50,177
Tells me I'm not meant to.

338
00:25:51,934 --> 00:25:54,980
Faith is a gift that
I have yet to receive.

339
00:26:01,691 --> 00:26:03,447
Be delicate with our treasures.

340
00:26:10,878 --> 00:26:12,587
- The archives are this way.
- Professor Langdon?

341
00:26:14,965 --> 00:26:17,689
If this path really leads to
the Church of Illumination,

342
00:26:18,111 --> 00:26:20,049
that may be where they've
hidden the antimatter.

343
00:26:20,235 --> 00:26:22,053
The shining star at the end
of the path. I thought so, too.

344
00:26:22,248 --> 00:26:25,175
Follow the path and we may find
the canister at the end of it.

345
00:26:25,358 --> 00:26:26,738
Can you deactivate the device?

346
00:26:26,935 --> 00:26:29,860
I can change the canister's batteries as long
as we have more than five minutes of life.

347
00:26:30,032 --> 00:26:33,212
That would give us another 24
hours to get it safely back to CERN.

348
00:26:36,376 --> 00:26:38,300
- Robert Langdon.
- Vittoria Vetra.

349
00:26:39,159 --> 00:26:42,645
Are you really a symbologist
or was he mocking you?

350
00:26:43,025 --> 00:26:44,822
No. Both. You're a physicist?

351
00:26:45,025 --> 00:26:47,695
Bioentanglement Physics.
The interconnective life systems?

352
00:26:47,696 --> 00:26:48,396
Okay.

353
00:26:49,583 --> 00:26:52,356
Your project... it was to give
towards the energy research?

354
00:26:52,641 --> 00:26:53,724
Eventually, yes.

355
00:26:53,926 --> 00:26:57,063
One pack of antimatter could
power an entire city for a month.

356
00:26:58,181 --> 00:26:59,996
Or tonight, I guess, destroy one.

357
00:27:01,800 --> 00:27:04,715
What are we looking for in the archives?
- A banned volume written by Galileo.

358
00:27:05,234 --> 00:27:08,814
- Galileo was Illuminati?
- Yeah, and an obedient Catholic.

359
00:27:09,288 --> 00:27:11,488
Who didn't think the church
and science were enemies

360
00:27:11,700 --> 00:27:13,930
but just a different language
telling the same story.

361
00:27:14,123 --> 00:27:15,685
Anyone of like minds could find
the Church of Illumination.

362
00:27:15,920 --> 00:27:20,181
But he couldn't exactly advertise its
location, so he created a coded path.

363
00:27:22,382 --> 00:27:24,736
Richter has started to turn
off the power at various rates.

364
00:27:25,015 --> 00:27:26,254
It will be back on in a minute.

365
00:27:27,837 --> 00:27:31,368
Then some unknown Illuminati
master sculpted four statues.

366
00:27:31,718 --> 00:27:34,203
Each one a tribute to one
of the fundamental elements:

367
00:27:34,402 --> 00:27:36,777
earth, air, fire, water.

368
00:27:36,987 --> 00:27:39,243
And placed the statues out in
public, in churches throughout Rome.

369
00:27:39,454 --> 00:27:42,303
Each statue held a clue
pointing to the next.

370
00:27:42,494 --> 00:27:44,838
At the end of the path was
the Church of Illumination.

371
00:27:45,038 --> 00:27:46,812
If you could find that,
you were one of them.

372
00:27:48,170 --> 00:27:50,710
What makes you think he's going to
murder the cardinals in the churches?

373
00:27:51,048 --> 00:27:55,823
The Illuminati called those four churches
by the special name "L'altare de la Scienza".

374
00:27:57,164 --> 00:27:59,418
Sacrifice them on the
altars of science, he said.

375
00:27:59,826 --> 00:28:00,723
Exactly.

376
00:28:04,579 --> 00:28:06,997
Oh, wow. Look at this.

377
00:28:31,073 --> 00:28:32,969
Excuse me. Signori.

378
00:28:35,508 --> 00:28:38,205
Cardinal Strauss, have you
been informed of the situation?

379
00:28:38,206 --> 00:28:38,950
Yeah.

380
00:28:39,261 --> 00:28:43,378
My belief is we should proceed
with the sealing of conclave.

381
00:28:43,486 --> 00:28:45,047
At this late hour?

382
00:28:45,416 --> 00:28:47,099
That would be highly unorthodox.

383
00:28:47,104 --> 00:28:50,612
And, yet, was ensured to wrought
my power in great elective.

384
00:28:50,655 --> 00:28:52,639
The cruelest honor in Christendom.

385
00:28:52,642 --> 00:28:55,703
I have no personal ambitions, Patrick.

386
00:28:55,819 --> 00:28:58,283
Only those I hold for my church.

387
00:28:58,289 --> 00:29:02,733
St. Peter's church, which is someday
taken at its most vulnerable moment.

388
00:29:02,734 --> 00:29:04,308
And this is not a coincidence.

389
00:29:04,309 --> 00:29:08,094
The church will not fall in a
day. We must evacuate Vatican City.

390
00:29:08,129 --> 00:29:12,594
That is exactly what they
want. Publicity and panic.

391
00:29:12,603 --> 00:29:16,186
No. We must not give them
oxygen for the media fire.

392
00:29:16,256 --> 00:29:19,233
But the people in St. Peter's Square?

393
00:29:19,268 --> 00:29:22,566
Care deeply about
their church, as we do.

394
00:29:22,681 --> 00:29:25,584
Their faith will sustain them.

395
00:29:25,588 --> 00:29:28,157
Their faith will not protect
them from an explosion.

396
00:29:29,790 --> 00:29:33,295
We are all bound for heaven
eventually, are we not?

397
00:29:34,264 --> 00:29:37,644
Spoken like one who has enjoyed the
blessings of a long and full life.

398
00:29:37,805 --> 00:29:42,500
Patrick, do not confuse the power
of the office you temporarily hold

399
00:29:42,504 --> 00:29:45,356
with your true place
here at the Vatican.

400
00:29:46,775 --> 00:29:49,910
You were a favorite of His Holiness.

401
00:29:49,935 --> 00:29:53,988
But His Holiness is with his father now.

402
00:29:55,750 --> 00:29:57,083
Mea culpa.

403
00:29:57,416 --> 00:29:59,406
Seal the doors.

404
00:30:13,181 --> 00:30:15,578
Everyone outside.

405
00:31:07,358 --> 00:31:08,505
This way, please.

406
00:31:09,539 --> 00:31:11,337
Oh. Beautiful.

407
00:31:15,731 --> 00:31:17,671
The chambers are hermetic vaults.

408
00:31:17,706 --> 00:31:21,900
Oxygen is kept at the lowest possible
level. It is a partial vacuum inside.

409
00:31:21,908 --> 00:31:24,220
So, extended stays are not recommended.

410
00:31:24,736 --> 00:31:28,088
So, don't panic if you
feel light headed at first.

411
00:31:39,481 --> 00:31:41,328
I'll be just outside the door,

412
00:31:41,606 --> 00:31:43,878
watching you, Mr. Langdon.

413
00:32:30,803 --> 00:32:33,871
Conclave will go on without us.

414
00:32:34,085 --> 00:32:37,070
It must. Now of all times.

415
00:32:37,185 --> 00:32:40,091
May God forgive you
for what you have done.

416
00:32:48,018 --> 00:32:50,221
Father, if God has issues,

417
00:32:50,607 --> 00:32:52,867
they won't be with what I've done.

418
00:32:54,033 --> 00:32:56,460
They will be with what I'm about to do.

419
00:33:17,228 --> 00:33:22,570
It was confiscated from the Netherlands
by the Vatican just after Galileo died.

420
00:33:22,605 --> 00:33:24,878
I've been petitioning to see it
for about ten years.

421
00:33:24,928 --> 00:33:26,596
Ever since I realized what was in it.

422
00:33:28,000 --> 00:33:29,963
What makes you so sure
that this thing is there?

423
00:33:30,364 --> 00:33:31,232
The number 503.

424
00:33:31,239 --> 00:33:35,458
I kept seeing it, over and over
again. In Illuminati letters.

425
00:33:35,763 --> 00:33:38,124
Scribbled in the margins.
Sometimes just signed '503'.

426
00:33:38,137 --> 00:33:40,448
It's a numeric clue, but, to what? Five?

427
00:33:40,452 --> 00:33:42,813
Well, that's a medieval
number to the Illuminati.

428
00:33:42,817 --> 00:33:46,064
There's the pentagram. Pythagoras.
Dozens of other examples in science.

429
00:33:46,066 --> 00:33:46,985
But what about 3?

430
00:33:47,052 --> 00:33:50,403
It didn't make sense, until I thought:
What if it's Roman numerals?

431
00:33:50,407 --> 00:33:54,343
DIII.
- D3. Galileo's third text.

432
00:33:54,378 --> 00:33:58,475
Dialogo. Discorso. Diagramma.

433
00:34:09,827 --> 00:34:13,348
Just a few days with this and I
could've actually finished my book.

434
00:34:13,384 --> 00:34:17,179
And sold dozens of copies
at the Harvard bookstore.

435
00:34:17,214 --> 00:34:19,308
Il Diagramma Veritatis.

436
00:34:19,475 --> 00:34:21,552
Diagram of Truth.

437
00:34:22,057 --> 00:34:24,405
I know about the
Dialogo and the Discorsi.

438
00:34:24,440 --> 00:34:28,333
Galileo laid out his theories about
the earth revolving around the sun.

439
00:34:28,368 --> 00:34:30,618
Right. It said the earth was not
the center of some universe

440
00:34:30,619 --> 00:34:31,725
with heaven above, hell below,

441
00:34:32,112 --> 00:34:33,561
as the church had said it was.

442
00:34:33,563 --> 00:34:35,905
So, they forced him to
recant his second book.

443
00:34:35,908 --> 00:34:37,081
But what was this one?

444
00:34:37,089 --> 00:34:38,835
This is how he got the word out.

445
00:34:38,836 --> 00:34:41,605
This is the truth. Not what
the Vatican forced him to write.

446
00:34:41,640 --> 00:34:45,280
Smuggled out of Rome, printed in
Holland on setched papyrus. See?

447
00:34:45,282 --> 00:34:47,947
That way, any scientist
that was caught with a copy

448
00:34:47,948 --> 00:34:51,638
could just throw it in water and
Galileo's heresy would disolve. Disappear.

449
00:34:51,673 --> 00:34:54,843
Between that and Vatican burnings

450
00:34:54,847 --> 00:34:58,000
it's possible this is the
only copy that remains.

451
00:34:58,079 --> 00:35:00,072
And if I'm correct,

452
00:35:00,121 --> 00:35:04,764
the segno is hidden on page number...

453
00:35:04,771 --> 00:35:06,046
Five.

454
00:35:07,014 --> 00:35:08,672
Yeah.

455
00:35:14,152 --> 00:35:16,442
Do you need help with the Latin?

456
00:35:17,032 --> 00:35:18,239
Sure.

457
00:35:24,864 --> 00:35:29,870
Movement of the planets,
elliptical orbits, idiosyntricity...

458
00:35:32,402 --> 00:35:36,048
Sorry. I don't think there's anything
that could be interpreted as a...

459
00:35:36,049 --> 00:35:36,959
Wait, wait, wait.

460
00:35:37,515 --> 00:35:38,696
Do that again.

461
00:35:40,840 --> 00:35:42,013
What is that?

462
00:35:44,665 --> 00:35:47,684
Wait. It's a watermark.
And there's a line of text.

463
00:35:47,817 --> 00:35:49,127
Go back.

464
00:35:50,813 --> 00:35:52,417
It's in English.

465
00:35:52,452 --> 00:35:54,000
English?

466
00:35:54,007 --> 00:35:55,369
Why English?

467
00:35:55,439 --> 00:35:58,643
English wasn't used in the
Vatican. It was too polluted.

468
00:35:58,649 --> 00:36:04,186
It's free thinking. It was the language
of radicals, like Shakespeare and Chaucer.

469
00:36:04,191 --> 00:36:04,948
Here's another one.

470
00:36:04,951 --> 00:36:10,072
"The path of light is laid a sacred test.
" Would you write this down as I dictate?

471
00:36:10,075 --> 00:36:11,875
Sorry, Professor. No time.

472
00:36:17,343 --> 00:36:19,031
Yeah, yeah.
Well, what the hell? Yeah.

473
00:36:35,066 --> 00:36:36,994
Twenty minutes till eight.
Where are we headed?

474
00:36:36,995 --> 00:36:39,057
Hold on. Hold on.
I'll tell you in a minute.

475
00:36:39,058 --> 00:36:40,478
Here. Let me see that page again.

476
00:36:46,637 --> 00:36:48,222
Where did you get that paper?

477
00:36:48,882 --> 00:36:50,209
We borrowed it.

478
00:36:50,245 --> 00:36:53,607
"From Santi's earthly tomb,
the demon's hole..."

479
00:36:53,608 --> 00:36:54,481
Are you insane?

480
00:36:54,483 --> 00:36:57,514
"...across Rome the mystic
elements unfold."

481
00:36:58,583 --> 00:37:01,549
"The path of light is
laid in a sacred test."

482
00:37:01,584 --> 00:37:04,253
"Let angels guide thee
on thy lofty quest."

483
00:37:05,083 --> 00:37:07,934
You removed a document
from the Vatican archives?

484
00:37:08,514 --> 00:37:09,590
She did.

485
00:37:14,258 --> 00:37:16,628
"From Santi's earthly tomb..."

486
00:37:16,632 --> 00:37:19,318
- The first marker is at Santi's tomb.
- Yeah.

487
00:37:19,592 --> 00:37:22,134
- But who's Santi?
