728
01:00:06,245 --> 01:00:08,303
Sure, I get that. It's also a bank.

729
01:00:19,132 --> 01:00:21,733
Commander Olivetti said that I was
not to leave your side this time.

730
01:00:24,847 --> 01:00:26,441
It wasn't me. It was her.

731
01:00:43,875 --> 01:00:46,011
Power in zone 3 is disabled.

732
01:00:46,478 --> 01:00:48,028
No response on the screen.

733
01:00:48,313 --> 01:00:50,426
Power on zone 3 again
and continue with zone 4.

734
01:01:01,779 --> 01:01:02,977
What sort of signs?

735
01:01:03,638 --> 01:01:05,235
I'm sorry?

736
01:01:09,727 --> 01:01:13,377
If the Holy Father was given
an overdose of Tinzaparin,

737
01:01:13,936 --> 01:01:15,954
what signs would his body bear?

738
01:01:17,769 --> 01:01:19,413
Bleeding of the oral mucosa.

739
01:01:21,094 --> 01:01:22,436
His tongue.

740
01:01:22,741 --> 01:01:26,056
Post-mortem, the blood congeals,
then turns the inside of the mouth black.

741
01:01:28,069 --> 01:01:29,928
Even after fourteen days?

742
01:01:30,766 --> 01:01:33,464
It wouldn't show up until at
least a week after his death.

743
01:01:38,599 --> 01:01:40,076
He was very important to me.

744
01:01:42,098 --> 01:01:43,624
Yeah, I understand.

745
01:01:48,433 --> 01:01:50,589
Will you come with me, please?

746
01:01:58,697 --> 01:02:00,463
Signore, would you
organize a security team

747
01:02:00,464 --> 01:02:02,349
to escort Ms. Vetra and
myself down to the crypt?

748
01:02:02,549 --> 01:02:04,318
Yes, sir. We'll leave immediately.

749
01:02:22,942 --> 01:02:24,835
Do you smoke?

750
01:02:26,267 --> 01:02:27,879
A little bit.

751
01:02:28,195 --> 01:02:31,118
You better sit down
before you keel over.

752
01:02:36,925 --> 01:02:41,775
What does this say in Italian?
Ecstasy of Saint Theresa. Right there.

753
01:02:44,347 --> 01:02:46,985
Moved at suggestion of the artist.

754
01:02:47,639 --> 01:02:51,729
Moved? To another church?
At the suggestion of Bernini?

755
01:02:51,765 --> 01:02:53,317
I don't know.

756
01:02:55,650 --> 01:02:59,948
Here. Translate all of this for me,
and I'll buy you a pack of smokes.

757
01:02:59,955 --> 01:03:02,592
I'm looking for a reference of fire.

758
01:03:04,528 --> 01:03:07,535
- Seraphim, meaning "the fiery one".
- Right.

759
01:03:10,006 --> 01:03:13,921
His great golden spear. A point of fire.

760
01:03:15,332 --> 01:03:19,338
Then "woman left completely afire."

761
01:03:19,375 --> 01:03:23,401
The ecstasy of Saint Theresa.
Saint Theresa on fire.

762
01:03:23,406 --> 01:03:26,055
So, this sculpture was
moved to this church?

763
01:03:27,706 --> 01:03:30,566
Why are they shuting down the system?
They know we're down here.

764
01:03:31,251 --> 01:03:34,216
If there's no power, there's no oxygen.

765
01:03:35,171 --> 01:03:37,783
- Can we get out?
- The door is electronic.

766
01:03:41,453 --> 01:03:43,207
Well, that's disappointing.

767
01:03:44,577 --> 01:03:47,571
- Where are we going?
- To see my father.

768
01:03:47,921 --> 01:03:49,402
I don't understand.

769
01:03:49,426 --> 01:03:52,222
I was orphaned when I
was nine years of age.

770
01:03:52,387 --> 01:03:56,853
A bombing in Ulster, the UVF protesting
the visit of a Catholic Archbishop.

771
01:03:56,933 --> 01:04:01,177
The Archbishop felt responsible
and he adopted me the following day.

772
01:04:01,438 --> 01:04:03,984
I was raised by him and by the Church.

773
01:04:04,554 --> 01:04:06,907
He was the wisest man I ever met.

774
01:04:07,368 --> 01:04:11,065
Even when I was young and stubborn,
I wanted to be ordained,

775
01:04:11,100 --> 01:04:14,541
but I was brought up in Italy
so I also wanted to do my military service.

776
01:04:14,546 --> 01:04:16,478
I wanted to fight.

777
01:04:16,915 --> 01:04:19,905
He told me, "Learn to fly."

778
01:04:19,938 --> 01:04:23,807
So, I joined the Aeronautica Militari.
Flew helicopters.

779
01:04:23,817 --> 01:04:26,219
Bringing the wounded back to hospitals.

780
01:04:26,224 --> 01:04:29,314
- He was a great man.
- Your father died.

781
01:04:30,179 --> 01:04:31,857
Fourteen days ago.

782
01:04:32,749 --> 01:04:34,644
Headquarters, you hear me?

783
01:04:35,182 --> 01:04:37,912
The flow is completed.
Oxygen level is very low.

784
01:04:37,913 --> 01:04:41,415
- Answer, please. Anybody hear me?
- Did you get anything?

785
01:04:41,423 --> 01:04:45,104
No. The walls are lead lined.
There's no signal.

786
01:07:59,535 --> 01:08:00,540
This way.

787
01:08:08,446 --> 01:08:12,426
If the Holy Father was murdered,
the implications are profound.

788
01:08:12,445 --> 01:08:14,754
Vatican security is impenetrable.

789
01:08:14,761 --> 01:08:17,303
No one from the outside
could've got anywhere near him.

790
01:08:17,676 --> 01:08:21,392
It was someone on the inside.
We can trust no one.

791
01:08:23,372 --> 01:08:27,318
On my screen, no response in zone 7.

792
01:08:27,357 --> 01:08:31,339
We rechon that the
battery will soon be empty

793
01:08:31,558 --> 01:08:33,821
and the device will explode
shortly before midnight.

794
01:08:55,451 --> 01:08:57,023
Holy Father...

795
01:08:57,963 --> 01:09:02,009
when I was young, you've told me the
voice in my heart was God's voice.

796
01:09:02,044 --> 01:09:05,467
You said I should follow
it no matter how painful.

797
01:09:05,474 --> 01:09:06,834
Forgive me.

798
01:09:08,544 --> 01:09:10,169
Please, give me strength.

799
01:09:11,354 --> 01:09:15,965
What I do, I do in the name
of everything you believed.

800
01:10:06,252 --> 01:10:08,087
God help us.

801
01:10:20,554 --> 01:10:23,321
Santa Maria della Vittoria.
Do you know it?

802
01:10:23,794 --> 01:10:26,207
- Yes, I do.
- It's the next church.

803
01:10:42,467 --> 01:10:44,321
I think someone just tried to kill me.

804
01:10:44,329 --> 01:10:46,517
Professor, I promise you,
we had no idea.

805
01:10:46,518 --> 01:10:47,729
- He knows I'm here?
- Yes.

806
01:10:47,730 --> 01:10:49,637
You heard me ask permission.
You gave me an escort.

807
01:10:49,642 --> 01:10:50,744
Yes, but we had no idea

808
01:10:50,745 --> 01:10:53,954
that portions of our white zones
were crosswired with that building.

809
01:10:54,948 --> 01:10:56,741
Commander Richter was
extending the search.

810
01:10:56,743 --> 01:10:58,606
If he had known the archives
were on that grid,

811
01:10:58,607 --> 01:10:59,965
he never would have killed the power.

812
01:11:01,027 --> 01:11:03,087
But there is the other possibility.

813
01:11:03,271 --> 01:11:06,172
Is it conceivable the Illuminati...

814
01:11:06,719 --> 01:11:09,203
have infiltrated the Swiss Guard?

815
01:11:11,846 --> 01:11:13,254
Perhaps.

816
01:11:23,392 --> 01:11:25,239
The journals. Where are they?

817
01:11:27,542 --> 01:11:29,867
Who took the journals from this desk?

818
01:11:39,992 --> 01:11:42,795
Signore, this is unacceptable.

819
01:11:43,492 --> 01:11:46,572
For a Camerlengo to enter the
chapel once conclave has begun.

820
01:11:46,579 --> 01:11:47,656
Forgive me.

821
01:11:47,657 --> 01:11:49,479
There's been a development.

822
01:12:00,037 --> 01:12:02,773
His Holiness Celestine was murdered!

823
01:12:02,774 --> 01:12:06,650
Is it so inconceivable
that it will happen again?

824
01:12:06,652 --> 01:12:09,553
Signori, please, a moment.
Please. Signori.

825
01:12:12,023 --> 01:12:14,467
Our church is at war.

826
01:12:15,540 --> 01:12:18,786
We are under attack from an old enemy.

827
01:12:19,145 --> 01:12:20,970
The Illuminati.

828
01:12:21,466 --> 01:12:23,986
They have struck us from within.

829
01:12:23,990 --> 01:12:26,186
Murdering our Holy Father!

830
01:12:26,221 --> 01:12:30,748
And threatening us all with destruction
at the hands of their new God 'Science'.

831
01:12:30,862 --> 01:12:34,109
They call it retribution.
They think it justified...

832
01:12:34,144 --> 01:12:38,291
because of the Church's attacks on men of
science in the distant past and it's true.

833
01:12:38,999 --> 01:12:44,064
Since the days of Galileo, this church has
tried to slow the relentless march of progress.

834
01:12:44,099 --> 01:12:46,333
Sometimes with misguided means.

835
01:12:47,842 --> 01:12:49,934
But science and
religion are not enemies.

836
01:12:51,550 --> 01:12:56,220
There are simply some things that
science is just too young to understand.

837
01:12:56,550 --> 01:12:58,396
So the Church pleads, "Stop."

838
01:12:58,930 --> 01:13:00,191
"Slow down."

839
01:13:00,373 --> 01:13:01,721
"Think. Wait."

840
01:13:01,900 --> 01:13:03,765
And, for this, they call us backwards.

841
01:13:04,884 --> 01:13:06,644
But who is more ignorant?

842
01:13:06,974 --> 01:13:08,978
The man who cannot define lightning...

843
01:13:09,341 --> 01:13:12,450
or the man who does not respect
its natural awesome power?

844
01:13:13,539 --> 01:13:15,685
The battle is well under way, signori.

845
01:13:16,419 --> 01:13:18,350
We must defend ourselves.

846
01:13:18,558 --> 01:13:21,127
But, what if this time, we fight
their stealth with openness?

847
01:13:21,302 --> 01:13:23,989
Combat their wicked
scheme with simple truth.

848
01:13:24,182 --> 01:13:27,133
And end this brutish
battle once and for all.

849
01:13:27,328 --> 01:13:30,142
If the outside world could
see this church as I do,

850
01:13:30,346 --> 01:13:32,241
looking beyond the
ritual of these walls,

851
01:13:32,438 --> 01:13:34,972
they would see a modern miracle.

852
01:13:35,182 --> 01:13:38,753
A brotherhood of
imperfect, simple souls...

853
01:13:38,948 --> 01:13:41,900
who want nothing more than to be voices of compassion

854
01:13:41,901 --> 01:13:43,794
in a world spinning out of control.

855
01:13:46,049 --> 01:13:48,476
Signori, I ask..

856
01:13:49,711 --> 01:13:51,440
I pray...

857
01:13:52,679 --> 01:13:54,961
that you break this conclave.

858
01:13:55,273 --> 01:13:56,629
Open the doors,

859
01:13:57,779 --> 01:13:59,508
evacuate St. Peter's Square

860
01:14:00,110 --> 01:14:01,804
and tell the world the truth.

861
01:14:37,332 --> 01:14:38,936
Get him down.

862
01:14:50,617 --> 01:14:53,089
There. There, that
chain. On that pulley.

863
01:14:53,309 --> 01:14:54,708
This bench. Get this pew off
here and make it a ladder.

864
01:16:16,729 --> 01:16:18,129
Vatican Police.

865
01:17:20,164 --> 01:17:22,895
My son...

866
01:17:22,930 --> 01:17:26,371
God answers all prayers, but...

867
01:17:27,173 --> 01:17:29,564
sometimes His answer is no.

868
01:17:30,737 --> 01:17:33,425
The College will not break conclave.

869
01:17:34,562 --> 01:17:38,563
May I suggest...
you direct your energies

870
01:17:38,564 --> 01:17:42,151
to helping the Swiss Guard
find this explosive device.

871
01:17:42,156 --> 01:17:43,828
If it exists.

872
01:17:45,008 --> 01:17:47,733
And leave Church leadership...

873
01:17:49,459 --> 01:17:51,282
to its leaders.

874
01:18:03,362 --> 01:18:04,592
Eminence.

875
01:18:06,854 --> 01:18:09,131
There is a growing fear

876
01:18:09,823 --> 01:18:11,980
that without the four Preferiti

877
01:18:11,985 --> 01:18:15,207
it defers much authority
for any candidate.

878
01:18:15,208 --> 01:18:16,964
It will not be possible,

879
01:18:17,279 --> 01:18:19,450
- unless...
- Speak plainly.

880
01:18:20,718 --> 01:18:24,449
It is the recommendation of many
that you asked to be removed...

881
01:18:24,455 --> 01:18:26,697
from your post as Great Elector.

882
01:18:26,972 --> 01:18:33,384
Thereby making yourself eligible
to wear the Ring of the Fisherman.

883
01:18:34,692 --> 01:18:37,952
Well, if it is God's will.

884
01:18:45,527 --> 01:18:47,525
May His will be done.

885
01:19:00,322 --> 01:19:02,243
Here! I hear someone.

886
01:19:04,523 --> 01:19:06,155
Remove the lid.

887
01:19:08,911 --> 01:19:09,965
Come on.

888
01:19:14,328 --> 01:19:15,919
Signore, are you okay?

889
01:19:24,223 --> 01:19:26,146
I know he is there.

890
01:19:26,158 --> 01:19:29,201
Madam, it is necessary
that you remain quiet.

891
01:19:29,217 --> 01:19:32,991
Don't tell me that I should remain calm.
I want to know what he will do.

892
01:19:37,540 --> 01:19:39,389
Commander, here's Ms. Vetra.

893
01:19:40,867 --> 01:19:43,412
Those journals are private property.
I demand that you return them to me.

894
01:19:43,414 --> 01:19:46,551
They're material evidence
in a Vatican investigation.

895
01:19:48,852 --> 01:19:49,998
I am an Italian citizen.

896
01:19:49,999 --> 01:19:52,767
My rights do not end just
because I crossed the other side.

897
01:19:52,768 --> 01:19:55,994
This is not Italy.
It's not even Rome. It's the Vatican.

898
01:19:56,019 --> 01:19:58,055
A country with its own laws.

899
01:19:58,059 --> 01:20:01,502
And when those journals passed the
border, they became my property.

900
01:20:01,507 --> 01:20:03,231
I will give them back to you

901
01:20:03,657 --> 01:20:06,688
when I've decided they contain
nothing of value to the investigation.

902
01:20:06,691 --> 01:20:09,027
Do you have something to
hide, Commandante Richter?

903
01:20:11,952 --> 01:20:13,890
Do you, Dr. Vetra?

904
01:20:35,516 --> 01:20:37,870
If it were up to me,
it wouldn't be this way.

905
01:20:39,518 --> 01:20:42,074
It's a sin to kill with pain.

906
01:20:43,324 --> 01:20:45,474
It's a sin to kill
without reason, Father.

907
01:20:51,763 --> 01:20:53,125
They made me a sinner.

908
01:21:12,877 --> 01:21:14,549
Saint Theresa on fire.

909
01:21:17,944 --> 01:21:18,925
Professor Langdon?

910
01:21:20,543 --> 01:21:22,695
- What direction is that?
- West, I think.

911
01:21:22,890 --> 01:21:24,705
"Across Rome the mystic
elements unfold."

912
01:21:26,848 --> 01:21:31,629
Piazza Barba Rini is here.
Saint Theresa is here.

913
01:21:32,544 --> 01:21:34,661
Where is the Santa Maria del Popolo,
the first altar of science?

914
01:21:34,869 --> 01:21:36,085
- Santa Maria del Popolo?
- Yes.

915
01:21:38,302 --> 01:21:39,464
Thank you.

916
01:21:40,339 --> 01:21:41,735
St. Peter's is here.

917
01:21:42,601 --> 01:21:44,074
We are here.

918
01:21:46,143 --> 01:21:47,748
A church with water.

919
01:21:49,800 --> 01:21:51,001
Wait. Wait, wait.

920
01:21:51,817 --> 01:21:53,195
Across Rome.

921
01:21:54,831 --> 01:21:57,138
The poem must mean it's
literally across Rome.

922
01:21:57,865 --> 01:21:58,414
Professor Langdon.

923
01:21:58,514 --> 01:22:01,177
Commander Richter has ordered me to
escort you to the Vatican immediately.

924
01:22:01,409 --> 01:22:05,969
Piazza Navona. Earth. Air. Fire. Water.

925
01:22:06,403 --> 01:22:08,142
"A-Cross" Rome.

926
01:22:08,695 --> 01:22:10,252
Bernini's Four Rivers.

927
01:22:11,891 --> 01:22:14,841
Professor Langdon, the Vatican insists
that I have to take you back immediately.

928
01:22:15,058 --> 01:22:17,301
The Vatican is about to see its
fourth cardinal murdered tonight.

929
01:22:17,505 --> 01:22:18,611
Now, look.

930
01:22:19,414 --> 01:22:22,239
You can do as they say and
force me back to the Vatican,

931
01:22:22,552 --> 01:22:24,833
where we can all mourn
his death together.

932
01:22:25,030 --> 01:22:27,097
Or you can show me how real cops act

933
01:22:27,327 --> 01:22:30,620
and take me to Piazza Navona,
where we still might be able to stop it.

934
01:22:34,336 --> 01:22:36,293
Oh. By all means, let's talk it over.

935
01:22:37,532 --> 01:22:39,225
In fourteen minutes,
he's going to be dead.

936
01:22:45,039 --> 01:22:46,578
Okay. This way, Professor.

937
01:22:55,288 --> 01:22:56,525
Yes, Padre?

938
01:22:56,935 --> 01:22:59,718
At 11:15, if the church
is still in peril,

939
01:23:00,856 --> 01:23:02,957
give the order to
evacuate the cardinals.

940
01:23:04,070 --> 01:23:05,491
But with dignity.

941
01:23:06,305 --> 01:23:09,207
Let them walk out into St. Peter's
Square with their heads held high.

942
01:23:10,171 --> 01:23:12,329
We don't want the last
image of this church to be

943
01:23:12,330 --> 01:23:14,400
of frightened old men
sneaking out the back door.

944
01:23:31,304 --> 01:23:32,634
"Where the angels guide thee..."

945
01:23:38,459 --> 01:23:40,252
There it is. There it is.

946
01:23:40,312 --> 01:23:42,880
Professor, I know this fountain.
There is no angel.

947
01:23:43,086 --> 01:23:45,346
The dove. The angel of peace.

948
01:23:45,927 --> 01:23:47,520
And it's looking in what direction?

949
01:23:48,277 --> 01:23:49,519
Uh... east, I think.

950
01:24:00,708 --> 01:24:03,613
Professor, just wait here. Stay put.

951
01:24:39,700 --> 01:24:41,339
Good evening. Can you help me?

952
01:24:42,346 --> 01:24:44,166
I need a doctor.

953
01:24:59,856 --> 01:25:01,034
Come here.

954
01:25:04,128 --> 01:25:05,225
Calm down. Don't shoot.

955
01:25:42,164 --> 01:25:44,124
Hey!

956
01:25:57,835 --> 01:25:59,984
Help! Somebody help!

957
01:26:37,875 --> 01:26:39,181
Help! Somebody!

958
01:27:50,738 --> 01:27:51,723
Cardinal Baja.

959
01:27:52,721 --> 01:27:53,652
Cardinal Baja.

960
01:27:54,318 --> 01:27:55,344
Si?

961
01:27:55,526 --> 01:27:57,172
Where was he hiding you?

962
01:27:58,170 --> 01:27:59,939
The Church of Illumination.
Where is it?

963
01:28:01,484 --> 01:28:03,742
Castel Sant'Angelo.

964
01:28:05,294 --> 01:28:07,095
Castle of the Angel.

965
01:28:28,543 --> 01:28:30,718
Sir, there's news about Cardinal Baja.

966
01:28:31,955 --> 01:28:34,816
The cardinal told Langdon he was
being held in Castel Sant'Angelo.

967
01:28:35,594 --> 01:28:37,644
If Langdon's right,
that's where the bomb is.

968
01:28:38,421 --> 01:28:40,872
- Send everyone we can spare.
- And you?

969
01:28:41,422 --> 01:28:42,476
I'm staying here.

970
01:28:55,647 --> 01:28:56,701
Vittoria.

971
01:28:58,065 --> 01:28:59,890
- You're all right?
- I'm all right, yes. What about you?

972
01:28:59,892 --> 01:29:01,668
I just heard about
Olivetti on the radio.

973
01:29:01,669 --> 01:29:02,641
I'm all right. I'm okay.

974
01:29:08,438 --> 01:29:10,579
Robert, we can't trust Richter.

975
01:29:10,583 --> 01:29:11,735
He took Silvano's journals.

976
01:29:11,736 --> 01:29:14,209
There must be something in
there he doesn't want us to see.

977
01:29:14,220 --> 01:29:16,348
The head of the Swiss Guard.

978
01:29:17,763 --> 01:29:20,472
From the Castel Sant'Angelo.
It's close enough so the wireless signal

979
01:29:20,473 --> 01:29:22,214
from that camera
could still reach the Vatican.

980
01:29:23,966 --> 01:29:26,854
The Church of Illumination
is somewhere here

981
01:29:27,386 --> 01:29:29,402
and your canister is inside it.

982
01:29:49,164 --> 01:29:50,605
Come with me.

983
01:29:54,649 --> 01:29:57,820
For 400 years, the Illuminati
met right under the Church's nose.

984
01:29:57,825 --> 01:30:00,981
The Vatican used this as a hideout
and as a prison for their enemies.

985
01:30:01,602 --> 01:30:05,551
If the explosion happens here, would
the blast radius take out the Vatican?

986
01:30:05,723 --> 01:30:08,315
And part of Rome along with it.

987
01:30:25,660 --> 01:30:27,298
They're pointing to it. The angels.

988
01:30:27,382 --> 01:30:29,317
The container must be down there.
Come on!

989
01:31:15,633 --> 01:31:18,735
- Where are they going?
- Back to search the other castle.

990
01:31:19,085 --> 01:31:20,781
No, no. It has to be here!

991
01:31:25,285 --> 01:31:26,985
Robert, it's a dead end.

992
01:31:27,390 --> 01:31:28,622
No, it's not.

993
01:31:29,044 --> 01:31:31,146
See if you can find a flashlight.

994
01:31:47,787 --> 01:31:50,142
All of these stones
are rectangular granite.

995
01:31:50,324 --> 01:31:52,594
Except right here. What is this?

996
01:31:56,830 --> 01:31:58,462
It's a pentagram.

997
01:31:58,623 --> 01:31:59,860
An eye...

998
01:32:00,411 --> 01:32:01,842
that leads to...

999
01:32:01,846 --> 01:32:03,002
Nowhere.

1000
01:32:12,369 --> 01:32:13,369
Robert?

1001
01:32:15,206 --> 01:32:18,274
These walls overlap and
there's a passageway in here.

1002
01:32:18,342 --> 01:32:19,723
Here. Let me have the flashlight.

1003
01:32:42,207 --> 01:32:45,249
It's a passageway that
leads to the Vatican.

1004
01:32:45,284 --> 01:32:47,748
An ancient escape route.

1005
01:32:50,031 --> 01:32:51,454
Oh, God.

1006
01:32:53,363 --> 01:32:54,451
Here.

1007
01:32:57,031 --> 01:32:58,751
Look.

1008
01:33:16,852 --> 01:33:20,252
(Final Payment in VW at Via Giulia)
(Key taped to driver side front wheel)

1009
01:33:30,251 --> 01:33:31,566
Get on the radio.

1010
01:33:31,567 --> 01:33:34,469
Get the word out.
Conclave remains sealed.

1011
01:33:34,473 --> 01:33:36,432
The Camerlengo gave the
order for evacuation at--

1012
01:33:36,593 --> 01:33:38,018
I'm counter-manning it.

1013
01:33:43,802 --> 01:33:45,791
This is it. This is their church.

1014
01:33:48,118 --> 01:33:50,799
The canister should be
lit by artificial light.

1015
01:34:13,843 --> 01:34:15,016
It's not here, Robert.

1016
01:34:15,066 --> 01:34:17,361
"The shining star at the end of the path."
It has to be.

1017
01:34:17,769 --> 01:34:19,520
It's not here.

1018
01:34:19,702 --> 01:34:21,857
What's the poem say?
- Nothing.

1019
01:34:21,908 --> 01:34:24,865
Nothing. It's all over.
There was just four lines,

1020
01:34:24,957 --> 01:34:27,000
each one describing...

1021
01:34:35,947 --> 01:34:37,695
There's a fifth brand.

1022
01:34:37,745 --> 01:34:39,776
It's not an ambigram.
It's just two crossed keys.

1023
01:34:40,177 --> 01:34:42,621
- The symbol for the Vatican.
- No.

1024
01:34:43,628 --> 01:34:46,813
No, the papacy.
They intend to kill him.

1025
01:34:46,848 --> 01:34:49,097
Before they destroy the Vatican,

1026
01:34:49,098 --> 01:34:51,004
they're going to brand
and kill the pope himself.

1027
01:34:51,054 --> 01:34:51,754
There is no pope.

1028
01:34:51,873 --> 01:34:53,629
"Tempo Sede Vacante."

1029
01:34:54,164 --> 01:34:55,865
The Camerlengo.

1030
01:34:57,505 --> 01:34:59,764
- We have to warn him.
- Take a step back, please.

1031
01:35:01,291 --> 01:35:03,513
Take your cell phone from your pocket.

1032
01:35:06,663 --> 01:35:08,404
Throw it in the fire.

1033
01:35:18,800 --> 01:35:20,625
Murderer.

1034
01:35:20,660 --> 01:35:22,584
You know, when they call me,

1035
01:35:23,234 --> 01:35:24,342
and they all call me,

1036
01:35:24,377 --> 01:35:25,956
it is so important to them

1037
01:35:25,963 --> 01:35:29,509
that I know that what they
ask is the Lord's will.

1038
01:35:29,514 --> 01:35:32,620
Or Allah's. Or Yahweh's.

1039
01:35:34,000 --> 01:35:35,859
And I suppose they're right.

1040
01:35:40,303 --> 01:35:44,344
Because if he was not vengeful,
I would not exist, now, would I?

1041
01:35:44,380 --> 01:35:47,099
I've had several chances
to eliminate you tonight.

1042
01:35:47,106 --> 01:35:49,398
You're still alive
because you have no weapon.

1043
01:35:49,399 --> 01:35:50,974
And they didn't ask me to kill you.

1044
01:35:50,979 --> 01:35:54,128
But if you pursue me,
it is another matter.

1045
01:36:01,063 --> 01:36:02,278
Be careful.

1046
01:36:02,446 --> 01:36:04,425
These are men of God.

1047
01:36:16,887 --> 01:36:18,084
The Camerlengo.

1048
01:36:26,106 --> 01:36:28,529
Have you come to make me a martyr?

1049
01:36:36,448 --> 01:36:37,462
Here. Here.

1050
01:38:01,133 --> 01:38:03,156
- I need to see the Camerlengo.
- He is not available.

1051
01:38:03,158 --> 01:38:05,690
- I demand to see the Camerlengo!
- He is not available.

1052
01:38:07,377 --> 01:38:08,759
We'll see about that.

1053
01:38:18,007 --> 01:38:20,619
Oh. It's a chiusa chiave.
It's a one way portal.

1054
01:38:20,659 --> 01:38:22,781
The only entrance is on the other side.

1055
01:38:23,334 --> 01:38:25,451
No. Hey! Help!

1056
01:38:33,530 --> 01:38:35,929
This is Robert Langdon and
Dr. Vetra. Open the door.

1057
01:38:48,806 --> 01:38:50,670
The Camerlengo is in danger.

1058
01:39:03,858 --> 01:39:06,414
He's the one. He's got a gun.

1059
01:39:09,882 --> 01:39:12,104
- Illuminatus!
- You bastard.

1060
01:39:12,673 --> 01:39:13,373
Illuminatus!

1061
01:39:13,507 --> 01:39:14,906
You bastard!

1062
01:39:22,744 --> 01:39:23,709
Padre?

1063
01:39:23,784 --> 01:39:27,237
Order the evacuation.
We only have nineteen minutes.

1064
01:39:30,978 --> 01:39:32,608
Here. He's...

1065
01:39:32,693 --> 01:39:34,994
And get the helicopter for
the older cardinals, right?

1066
01:39:34,995 --> 01:39:35,695
Yes, sir.

1067
01:39:48,913 --> 01:39:49,926
Robert?

1068
01:39:50,089 --> 01:39:52,848
The brand, the symbol.
Could it have another meaning?

1069
01:39:59,184 --> 01:40:02,382
Crossed keys,
but those were upside down.

1070
01:40:02,417 --> 01:40:03,982
St. Peter.

1071
01:40:04,870 --> 01:40:06,671
The first pope...

1072
01:40:07,774 --> 01:40:10,643
...was crucified upside down.
- On Vatican Hill.

1073
01:40:10,649 --> 01:40:13,512
- A few hundred feet below us.
- Necropolis. City of the dead.

1074
01:40:13,514 --> 01:40:16,158
"Upon this rock, I
will build my church."

1075
01:40:16,162 --> 01:40:18,688
"Or bring it down upon itself."

1076
01:40:19,464 --> 01:40:22,682
The bomb. It's in St. Peter's tomb.

1077
01:40:37,096 --> 01:40:38,635
The grid is still cycling.

1078
01:40:38,636 --> 01:40:40,541
The power to this section must be down.

1079
01:41:26,208 --> 01:41:29,012
It must be here. It must be.

1080
01:41:39,806 --> 01:41:40,977
Don't touch it.

1081
01:41:42,482 --> 01:41:44,032
We have seven minutes.

1082
01:41:49,942 --> 01:41:52,139
Robert, hold this.

1083
01:42:31,443 --> 01:42:33,893
It's cold down here, isn't it?

1084
01:42:33,897 --> 01:42:35,256
What's wrong?

1085
01:42:35,343 --> 01:42:37,879
Cold decreases battery life.

1086
01:42:39,877 --> 01:42:43,202
- We may have less than five minutes.
- So?

1087
01:42:43,237 --> 01:42:46,134
If I pull the power with
less than five minutes...

1088
01:42:46,139 --> 01:42:49,070
the residual charge
won't hold suspension.

1089
01:42:50,185 --> 01:42:52,098
We should leave it here
and get clear if we can.

1090
01:42:52,099 --> 01:42:53,269
At least down here the damage--

1091
01:42:53,270 --> 01:42:54,602
No!

1092
01:42:56,065 --> 01:42:57,532
- No. Wait!
- Father!

1093
01:43:00,053 --> 01:43:02,086
We are live here at
St. Peter's Square...

1094
01:43:02,090 --> 01:43:05,382
where, despite a bomb threat,
and an orderly evacuation,

1095
01:43:05,389 --> 01:43:08,074
the crowd is actually growing in size.

1096
01:43:08,079 --> 01:43:10,875
As we await an official announcement
from the Vatican spokesman

1097
01:43:10,880 --> 01:43:12,965
as to the exact nature of the threat

1098
01:43:12,969 --> 01:43:15,944
and whether or not they are
treating it as a credible danger...

1099
01:43:24,098 --> 01:43:25,002
This way!

1100
01:43:54,170 --> 01:43:55,383
He's got a bomb with him.

1101
01:43:56,621 --> 01:43:57,682
A bomb?

1102
01:44:02,947 --> 01:44:05,504
Roberto, this is an emergency.
I'll take her up alone.

1103
01:44:10,219 --> 01:44:12,269
He's got clearance.

1104
01:44:35,814 --> 01:44:38,376
Oh, my God.

1105
01:46:34,912 --> 01:46:36,553
Get down!

1106
01:49:21,828 --> 01:49:23,152
Cardinal Strauss?

1107
01:49:23,952 --> 01:49:27,527
It was the Camerlengo.
He has saved us all.

1108
01:49:28,120 --> 01:49:31,248
He has saved the Church
and he's still alive.

1109
01:49:32,606 --> 01:49:34,617
Praise God. Praise God.

1110
01:49:39,889 --> 01:49:41,130
He is alive.

1111
01:49:41,642 --> 01:49:44,378
He sacrificed himself for all of us.

1112
01:50:11,566 --> 01:50:14,341
You know the worst thing
we thought would happen

1113
01:50:15,517 --> 01:50:18,831
was that our work would fall into
the hands of the energy companies.

1114
01:50:21,573 --> 01:50:23,300
We thought we could change the world.

1115
01:50:24,178 --> 01:50:27,964
- So naive.
- No, not naive.

1116
01:50:29,074 --> 01:50:30,545
Innocent, maybe.

1117
01:50:31,114 --> 01:50:33,252
But it's not a crime.

1118
01:50:34,702 --> 01:50:36,090
I'm not so sure.

1119
01:50:38,148 --> 01:50:39,906
Go back to work.

1120
01:50:41,101 --> 01:50:42,685
Change the world.

1121
01:51:02,779 --> 01:51:08,382
A gift, uh, you understand?
Let's say for Catholics everywhere.

1122
01:51:08,595 --> 01:51:11,255
The Carmelengo's age
shouldn't influence the decision.

1123
01:51:11,434 --> 01:51:14,191
Signori, you are no doubt
aware that by Holy Law

1124
01:51:14,192 --> 01:51:17,004
the man is inelligible
for election to the papacy.

1125
01:51:17,340 --> 01:51:19,327
He's not a cardinal.
He's a priest.

1126
01:51:19,328 --> 01:51:20,597
He's of insufficient age.

1127
01:51:20,807 --> 01:51:23,678
Or maybe there's a way we
could consider the possibility.

1128
01:51:23,871 --> 01:51:27,839
I am sorry. The protocols of conclave
are not subject to modification.

1129
01:51:28,008 --> 01:51:30,826
I will not call a ballot on this matter.

1130
01:51:31,032 --> 01:51:33,608
But, signore, you
would not hold a ballot.

1131
01:51:33,811 --> 01:51:37,184
Surely, you remember? You gave
up your post as Great Elector.

1132
01:51:37,921 --> 01:51:40,064
They are singing at St. Peter's Square.

1133
01:51:40,252 --> 01:51:42,888
Now, what happened here
tonight transcends our laws.

1134
01:51:43,108 --> 01:51:47,344
Has it? Is it God's will that
we give ourselves over to frenzy?

1135
01:51:47,448 --> 01:51:48,879
Discard the rules of the Church?

1136
01:51:48,919 --> 01:51:51,119
Perhaps we need not discard them.

1137
01:51:52,145 --> 01:51:57,747
Signori, I am thinking now of Romano
Pontifici Eligendo numero 60...

1138
01:51:57,987 --> 01:52:00,881
- Acclamation by Adoration.
- Exactly, signore. Exactly.

1139
01:52:01,150 --> 01:52:03,605
Yes. If the Holy Spirit
speaks through us,

1140
01:52:04,126 --> 01:52:06,026
and we call a man's name out loud...

1141
01:52:06,220 --> 01:52:08,972
That is election by adoration.

1142
01:52:09,402 --> 01:52:11,229
- Yes.
- He's God's choice.

1143
01:52:11,509 --> 01:52:17,248
Yes. And the candidate need only be
an ordained member of the clergy,

1144
01:52:17,252 --> 01:52:21,338
present in the Sistine Chapel
at the moment of his election.

1145
01:52:53,080 --> 01:52:55,375
- Signor Camerlengo?
- Yes?

1146
01:52:55,376 --> 01:52:58,857
The cardinals ask you to join them
in conclave as soon as possible.

1147
01:52:58,942 --> 01:53:01,434
- Me?
- Yes, Padre.

1148
01:53:24,525 --> 01:53:25,947
What are you doing?

1149
01:53:25,997 --> 01:53:28,342
Silvano's journals. I want them back.

1150
01:53:52,572 --> 01:53:54,045
Richter said...

1151
01:53:55,366 --> 01:53:57,700
His Holiness suffered from seizures

1152
01:53:57,705 --> 01:54:00,212
and steps were taken...

1153
01:54:00,421 --> 01:54:02,319
for safety.

1154
01:54:06,324 --> 01:54:08,869
He made sure he was watched, he said.

1155
01:54:10,952 --> 01:54:13,895
What if he were trying
to give me this key?

1156
01:54:15,059 --> 01:54:17,026
That's the Papal office.

1157
01:54:17,460 --> 01:54:19,342
If the Pope was worried about seizures,

1158
01:54:19,343 --> 01:54:22,286
he must've had Richter install
cameras without telling anyone.

1159
01:54:22,321 --> 01:54:25,123
To keep an eye on him for his safety.

1160
01:54:26,886 --> 01:54:28,861
Maybe it records.

1161
01:54:38,927 --> 01:54:43,572
- I read the journals, Patrick.
- The scientist kept journals. So?

1162
01:54:43,573 --> 01:54:46,939
- You figure prominently in them.
- Really?

1163
01:54:46,941 --> 01:54:51,541
The Devoli wasn't just a physicist.
He was also a Catholic priest.

1164
01:54:52,239 --> 01:54:56,405
As such, he was deeply conflicted
about the implications of his work

1165
01:54:56,406 --> 01:54:58,426
and in need of spiritual guidance.

1166
01:54:58,434 --> 01:55:00,198
Like Galileo.

1167
01:55:01,039 --> 01:55:02,845
About a month ago,

1168
01:55:02,849 --> 01:55:05,180
he requested an
audience with the Pope.

1169
01:55:05,181 --> 01:55:06,113
But you know that,

1170
01:55:06,305 --> 01:55:09,586
cause you granted the audience and
you were also present during it.

1171
01:55:09,588 --> 01:55:12,766
The 'God Particle'. To actually
claim an act of creation.

1172
01:55:12,767 --> 01:55:17,154
- The blasphemy. The arrogance.
- The Holy Father didn't see it like that.

1173
01:55:17,259 --> 01:55:19,359
He urged him to go public.

1174
01:55:19,364 --> 01:55:22,071
His Holiness thought that
the discovery could actually

1175
01:55:22,172 --> 01:55:25,408
scientifically prove the
existence of a divine power.

1176
01:55:25,411 --> 01:55:28,614
And begin to bridge the gap
between science and religion.

1177
01:55:28,618 --> 01:55:31,220
His work was not religious.
It was sacrilegious.

1178
01:55:31,222 --> 01:55:32,034
But you...

1179
01:55:32,924 --> 01:55:36,664
You saw the pope's position
as a softening of church law.

1180
01:55:36,669 --> 01:55:40,484
As an old man's weakness.
Your father's weakness.

1181
01:55:40,519 --> 01:55:42,245
You murdered the Vicar of Christ.

1182
01:55:42,246 --> 01:55:44,337
He raised me to
protect this Church,

1183
01:55:44,340 --> 01:55:45,923
even from within.

1184
01:55:47,667 --> 01:55:52,250
Then you conjured up an old enemy
from the past. The Illuminati.

1185
01:55:52,285 --> 01:55:54,786
You found the ancient brands
in the papal vaults

1186
01:55:54,787 --> 01:55:57,325
and put them to use
to spread fear!

1187
01:55:57,326 --> 01:55:59,792
The Cardinals are men of belief.

1188
01:55:59,829 --> 01:56:03,815
Right now, their belief
in evil is uniting them.

1189
01:56:03,820 --> 01:56:06,815
The entire Catholic world
will be united by this attack.

1190
01:56:06,820 --> 01:56:08,402
There is no attack.

1191
01:56:09,362 --> 01:56:12,588
You're trying to convince the
Cardinals they're in a war,

1192
01:56:12,593 --> 01:56:14,438
so they will choose a
warrior to lead them.

1193
01:56:14,442 --> 01:56:15,876
We are at war.

1194
01:56:15,878 --> 01:56:17,915
We're weak when we should be strong.

1195
01:56:17,919 --> 01:56:21,814
If science is allowed to
claim the power of creation,

1196
01:56:21,828 --> 01:56:23,586
what is left for God?

1197
01:56:23,621 --> 01:56:25,545
It didn't work, Patrick.

1198
01:56:26,233 --> 01:56:29,219
- It isn't finished.
- Oh yes, it's finished.

1199
01:56:31,491 --> 01:56:32,882
It's finished.

1200
01:56:33,740 --> 01:56:36,945
I've shown the journals
to Father Simeon.

1201
01:56:36,951 --> 01:56:39,131
The moment the doors
to the Conclave open,

1202
01:56:39,137 --> 01:56:41,292
he will tell the Cardinals
what you've done.

1203
01:56:42,181 --> 01:56:44,391
I was planning on doing this alone.

1204
01:56:47,666 --> 01:56:48,850
Put it down.

1205
01:56:51,865 --> 01:56:53,892
But, perhaps,
it's better that you're here.

1206
01:56:53,939 --> 01:56:55,320
Put it down.

1207
01:56:57,219 --> 01:56:58,956
Put it away.

1208
01:57:10,024 --> 01:57:13,620
Help. He's the one.
He's got a gun.

1209
01:57:17,264 --> 01:57:19,696
- Illuminatus!
- You bastard.

1210
01:57:20,053 --> 01:57:20,815
Illuminatus!

1211
01:57:20,821 --> 01:57:21,967
You bastard!

1212
01:57:26,046 --> 01:57:27,153
Padre.

1213
01:57:37,055 --> 01:57:40,223
And get the helicopter for
the older cardinals, right?

1214
01:58:29,671 --> 01:58:32,214
I've been summoned by
the College of Cardinals.

1215
01:59:42,237 --> 01:59:43,556
Gently.

1216
01:59:43,864 --> 01:59:45,238
But within our walls.

1217
01:59:57,360 --> 01:59:59,823
He's on your side.

1218
02:00:46,153 --> 02:00:50,061
Father, into thy hands
I commend my spirit.

1219
02:01:37,960 --> 02:01:42,550
Church sources now confirm that
Carmelengo, Father Patrick McKenna,

1220
02:01:42,551 --> 02:01:46,600
has died of internal injuries
sustained in his heroic fall...

1221
02:01:47,920 --> 02:01:51,878
The Catholic church thanks
Camerlengo for his selfless act

1222
02:01:51,879 --> 02:01:54,360
and demands his
immediate canonization.

1223
02:01:54,440 --> 02:01:57,324
The Vatican has also confirmed
the deaths of three Cardinals

1224
02:01:57,325 --> 02:01:59,451
and the fire in the
Santa Maria della Vittoria.

1225
02:01:59,546 --> 02:02:03,821
As we await the appearance of the new
Holy Father Cardinal Baggia of Italy,

1226
02:02:03,950 --> 02:02:05,525
one of the four original Preferiti,

1227
02:02:06,033 --> 02:02:08,174
who, despite terrorist
attempts at disruption

1228
02:02:08,214 --> 02:02:09,759
seems to have been selected

1229
02:02:09,760 --> 02:02:13,822
in one of the swiftest and smoothest
conclaves in modern church history.

1230
02:02:20,916 --> 02:02:22,669
Professor Langdon? Please.

1231
02:02:38,403 --> 02:02:41,859
A token of thanks from His Holiness

1232
02:02:42,361 --> 02:02:44,599
and from his new Camerlengo.

1233
02:02:46,073 --> 02:02:48,828
We are grateful you saved his life.

1234
02:02:48,937 --> 02:02:52,465
And it's our understanding
that you require this text

1235
02:02:52,470 --> 02:02:54,965
to complete your scholary work.

1236
02:02:56,197 --> 02:03:00,998
We ask only that in your
last grand testament

1237
02:03:01,067 --> 02:03:03,861
you ensure it finds its way home.

1238
02:03:06,274 --> 02:03:07,623
Of course.

1239
02:03:07,841 --> 02:03:09,811
And when you write of us,

1240
02:03:09,934 --> 02:03:12,583
and you will write of us,

1241
02:03:12,832 --> 02:03:14,776
may I ask one thing?

1242
02:03:15,273 --> 02:03:16,996
Do so gently.

1243
02:03:19,048 --> 02:03:20,485
I'll try.

1244
02:03:20,781 --> 02:03:22,485
Religion is flawed,

1245
02:03:23,158 --> 02:03:26,063
but only because man is flawed.

1246
02:03:26,067 --> 02:03:28,681
All men, including this one.

1247
02:03:43,225 --> 02:03:45,177
He chose the name Luke.

1248
02:03:47,787 --> 02:03:50,862
There's been many Marks and Johns.

1249
02:03:51,967 --> 02:03:53,843
Never a Luke.

1250
02:03:54,208 --> 02:03:56,337
It said he was a doctor.

1251
02:03:56,781 --> 02:04:00,301
It's quite a message.
Science and faith, all in one.

1252
02:04:01,206 --> 02:04:03,273
The world is in need of both.

1253
02:04:04,983 --> 02:04:07,126
You'll counsel him wisely.

1254
02:04:07,981 --> 02:04:10,774
I'm an old man.
I'll counsel him briefly.

1255
02:04:16,600 --> 02:04:18,466
Mr. Langdon.

1256
02:04:23,489 --> 02:04:28,210
Thanks be to God for sending
someone to protect this church.

1257
02:04:32,141 --> 02:04:35,483
I don't believe He sent me, Father.

1258
02:04:35,544 --> 02:04:37,104
Oh, my son.

1259
02:04:37,566 --> 02:04:39,485
Of course He did.

